# Student Course Registration System

A full-stack web application that allows students to register, log in, view available courses, and enroll in them online.
The system provides a responsive and user-friendly interface built using modern web technologies and stores data in a MongoDB database.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

The **Student Course Registration System** is designed to simplify the process of course enrollment in colleges or educational institutions. Students can create accounts, log in securely, browse available courses, and enroll in them through an interactive web interface.

The application uses **Node.js and Express.js** for the backend, **MongoDB** for database management, and **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** for the frontend interface.

---

## 🚀 Features

* Student Registration
* Student Login Authentication
* View Available Courses
* Enroll in Courses
* Dynamic content updates using JavaScript
* REST API communication using Fetch API
* MongoDB database integration
* Responsive user interface

